Hello! Thank you for calling Strike Lanes Bowling Alley. My name is Alex. How can I assist you today?

Hi Alex. I'm trying to understand a charge on my latest bill.

Of course! Could I have your name to better assist you?

Sure, my name is Jamie.

Thank you, Jamie. Could I get your account number, please?

My account number is one two three four five.

Great, and for verification purposes, could you provide the last four digits of the phone number associated with your account?

Sure, it's seven eight nine zero.

Thank you, Jamie. I’ve found your account. Let me check the billing details... I see here that the charge you're questioning is for a group lane reservation. It was processed on the last Friday of the month.

Oh, I remember now. Thanks for clarifying that, Alex.

No problem, Jamie. Thank you for your time today, and for choosing Strike Lanes Bowling Alley. Have a great day!
